responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "8F7A4C114199BD6969266381A39F0BA2", "No I haven\'t, just bits of gossip here and there, but I mostly keep to myself. I have heard though that there\'s some funny business about his so-called noble heritage. Some say he ain\'t a politician at all, and he just happened upon a prize earnings, but I reckon he earned his early fortune back home, and bought his wares here to contend for mayorship.")
